| Plot Type                | Function Example           |
| ------------------------ | -------------------------- |
| Exposure–Response        | `plot_exposure_response()` |
| Dose–Response curves     | `plot_dose_response()`     |
| Decision bands           | `plot_decision_band()`     |
| PTA heatmaps             | `plot_pta_heatmap()`       |
| Spaghetti + IQR overlays | `plot_longitudinal()`      |
| Forest plots             | `plot_forest()`            |
| Swimmer plots            | `plot_swimmer()`           |
| Waterfall plots          | `plot_waterfall()`         |
| Stacked bar for safety   | `plot_safety_stack()`      |
| KM curves with censoring | `plot_km()`                |

| Plot Type          | Description                                             | Function Name              |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| Benefit-Risk grid  | 2D decision space for efficacy vs. safety probabilities | `plot_benefit_risk_grid()` |
| Traffic light plot | Green/yellow/red indicators by dose and endpoint        | `plot_traffic_light()`     |
